name: Roll Rate
description: Measured Roll Rate using orthogonally mounted angular rate sensors; in platform coordinates  + Roll Platform South (Starboard) Down

name: Pitch Rate
description: Measured Pitch Rate using orthogonally mounted angular rate sensors; in platform coordinates  + Pitch Platform East (Bow) Down

name: Yaw Rate
description: Measured yaw rate using orthogonally mounted angular rate sensors; in platform coordinates + Yaw Bow to Port

name: Surge Acc
description: Measured surge acceleration using biaxial accelerometers

name: Sway Acc
description: Measured sway acceleration using biaxial accelerometers

name: Heave Acc
description: Measured heave acceleration using vertical accelerometer

name: Surge Temp
description: Measured internal surge acceleration temperature used to correct temperature sensitive linear accelerometer using algorithm from manufacturer

name: Sway Temp
description: Measured internal sway acceleration temperature used to correct temperature sensitive linear accelerometer using algorithm from manufacturer

name: Heave Temp
description: Measured internal heave acceleration temperature used to correct temperature sensitive linear accelerometer using algorithm from manufacturer

name: Latitude DegMin
description: Latitude Degrees and Integer Minutes only (raw data – not for general use)

name: Latitude DecMin
description: Latitude Decimal minutes only. 1 to 4 decimal places (0 - 0.XXXX minutes (raw data - not for general use))

name: Longitude DegMin
description: Longitude Degrees and Integer Minutes only (raw data – not for general use)

name: Longitude DecMin
description: Longitude Decimal Minutes only. 1 to 4 decimal places (0 - 0.XXXX minutes (raw data - not for general use))

name: Number of Satillites
description: number of satellites being used to compute the position by the GPS receiver

name: True Heading
description: direction the platform is pointing, measured in degrees relative to true north

name: Wind Speed
description: Wind Speed in mph measured at the wind sensor mounting location
comments: Height of EPRMS wind sensor is 168.66ft from MWL for Gunnison / Wind speed units are in mph

name: Wind Direction
description: Wind direction FROM measured in degrees at the wind sensor mounting location relative to sensor's pointing direction
comments: Height of EPRMS wind sensor is 168.66ft from MWL for Gunnison / Wind speed units are in mph

name: North Ballast Level
description: Water level in the ballast tank

name: South Ballast Level
description: Water level in the ballast tank

name: East Ballast Level
description: Water level in the ballast tank

name: West Ballast Level
description: Water level in the ballast tank

name: Draft
description: Vertical distance from the waterline to the lowest point of the platform

name: VADCP Max Curr Spd
description: Maximum of surface current across the vertical water profile measured in knots during observation interval near the platform, as measured by the ADCP
comments: Bin settings of 1 to 42 used for Gunnison VDCP to obtain maximum

name: VADCP Max Curr Dir
description: Surface current direction TOWARDS relative to True North during observation interval near the platform, corresponding to the maxumum current across water profile as measured by the ADCP.
comments: Bin settings of 1 to 42 used for Gunnison VDCP to obtain maximum

name: Latitude
description: Calculated Latitude using DegMin, DecMin as measured at GPS

name: Longitude
description: Calculated Longitude using DegMin, DecMin as measured at GPS

name: Easting
description: Eastings at the GPS antenna location, measured from platform reference position

name: Northing
description: Northings at the GPS antenna location, measured from platform reference position

name: Surge Acc COR
description: Measured surge accelerations corrected for temperature using the algorithm from the manufacturer

name: Sway Acc COR
description: Measured sway accelerations corrected for temperature using the algorithm from the manufacturer

name: Heave Acc COR
description: Measured heave accelerations corrected for temperature using the algorithm from the manufacturer

name: Spar Roll
description: Remove mean from the measured roll rate; integrate using trapezoidal rule

name: Spar Pitch
description: Remove mean from the measured pitch rate; integrate using trapezoidal rule

name: 15 Min Avg Spar Roll
description: 15 minute running average of spar roll

name: 15 Min Avg Spar Pitch
description: 15 minute running average of spar pitch

name: Expected 1 Hr Max Roll
description: Predicted maximum roll angle expected within the next hour

name: Expected 1 Hr Max Pitch
description: Predicted maximum pitch angle expected within the next hour

name: Platform Heading
description: platform's current orientation or facing direction

name: Riser A Bend Abt X-Axis
description: Bending angle of Riser around the X-axis

name: Riser A Bend Abt Y-Axis
description: Bending angle of Riser around the Y-axis

name: Riser B Bend Abt X-Axis
description: Bending angle of Riser around the X-axis

name: Riser B Bend Abt Y-Axis
description: Bending angle of Riser around the Y-axis

description: Bending angle of Riser around the X-axis

description: Bending angle of Riser around the Y-axis

description: Bending angle of Riser around the X-axis

description: Bending angle of Riser around the X-axis

description: Bending angle of Riser around the Y-axis

description: Bending angle of Riser around the X-axis

description: Bending angle of Riser around the Y-axis

description: Bending angle of Riser around the X-axis
